 `<account_id>:<workload_id>:<guid>`, e.g.

bash

```sh
$ pulumi import newrelic:plugins/workload:Workload foo 12345678:1456:MjUyMDUyOHxBUE18QVBRTElDQVRJT058MjE1MDM3Nzk1
```

